skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eyemed
des:
With more than 47 million members, EyeMed Vision Care is America’s fastest-growing vision benefits company. Driven to become the nation’s first choice for vision benefits, EyeMed is focused on providing the innovative benefit solutions members appreciate most, so they can see life to the fullest. EyeMed offers a large and diverse network of independent and retail providers and believes members deserve the experience of benefits made easy.

You can say "Alexa, open EyeMed." then follow the prompts Alexa gives you from there. 

Or say "Alexa, ask EyeMed..."

“Who is EyeMed?”
“What makes EyeMed different?”
“Who is in your network?”
“How is your network innovating?”
“What can you get with your benefit?”
“How do you control out-of-pocket costs?”
“How do you make it easy for members?”
“How do you make it easy for clients?”
